ngly rare as this is the first time I saw it drop and I killed her a quite a lot. I tried to open doors with it but it did not work so the item alone is not a key. Clicking on it did not do anything. Anyone else have seen it drop? I cant find this item listed anywhere. Is this one of the components needed to make the master key?<br>
