Narith Trumystic<br>
Brell Serilis <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubloodshard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bloodshard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/2/01 1:34:20 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> VS is KOS</span><hr size=1> I even had ally faction with Venril Sathir (Overthere faction) in the past &amp; I still conned KOS to Venril Sathir himself.<br>
